OL,3,GOPINIONCBBC One takes wrong turn in
OL,4,Cpeak time
OL,5,
OL,6,FAs far as flops go, they do not come
OL,7,Fmuch bigger.
OL,9,FStranded on Honeymoon Island has
OL,10,Fattracted some of the lowest peak time
OL,11,Fratings ever recorded for BBC One.
OL,13,FAnd, worse, it straddles the key 9pm
OL,14,Fslot three nights a week.
OL,16,FIf an ITV 1 show was struggling to
OL,17,Fattract 0.5m viewers, there's every
OL,18,Fchance it would be unceremoniously
OL,19,Fpulled.
