OL,3,GOPINIONCBBC One takes wrong turn in
OL,4,Cpeak time
OL,5,
OL,6,FNow, of course, the overnights are not
OL,7,Feverything - the programme's
OL,8,Fperformance also needs to be judged on
OL,9,Fits success on iPlayer.
OL,11,FBut it is undeniably a flop on BBC One.
OL,13,FThis begs two questions.
OL,15,FI would argue it had no place on BBC
OL,16,FOne full stop.
OL,18,FThe role of BBC One is to bring wide,
OL,19,Fdisparate groups of people together.
