OL,3,GOPINIONCBBC One takes wrong turn in
OL,4,Cpeak time
OL,5,
OL,6,FThis programme simply feels out of
OL,7,Fplace on One. It is simply - at least
OL,8,Fon the surface - not what you would
OL,9,Fexpectto see there.
OL,11,FWhether it should have been
OL,12,Fcommissioned at all is a more nuanced
OL,13,Fmatter.
OL,15,FAll audiences deserve to be served by
OL,16,Fthe BBC. Everyone should get value from
OL,17,Ftheir licence fee.
OL,19,FBut surely that means trying to serve
OL,20,Fall audiences with something of
OL,21,Foriginality and value.
