OL,3,GOPINIONCBBC One takes wrong turn in
OL,4,Cpeak time
OL,5,
OL,6,FThis programme - at least superficially
OL,7,F- seemed derivative. If AI was used to
OL,8,Fsuggest formats to cynically attract an
OL,9,Faudience which is underserved by the
OL,10,FBBC, this is the kind of thing it might
OL,11,Fcook up.
OL,13,FThis matters.
OL,15,FThe BBC's charter is up for renewal.
OL,17,FThere needs to be a debate over just
OL,18,Fwhat the BBC is for.
