OL,3,GOPINIONCBBC One takes wrong turn in
OL,4,Cpeak time
OL,5,
OL,6,FI would always defend the need for the
OL,7,FBBC to have popular drama and
OL,8,Fentertainment.
OL,10,FThe BBC does not exist just to produce
OL,11,Fserious and innovative programmes or
OL,12,Fprovide what the market cannot
OL,13,Fdeliver.
OL,15,FBut there need to be no go areas too.
OL,17,FFor instance, certain derivative or
OL,18,Fbought in formats where there is little
OL,19,Fsense of adding public value.
